{"tid":1200982,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普:已安排G20峰會上與習近平會談","createTime":"2019-06-11T01:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T21:41:20.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6471d1fd567160d3345620fa892554dd9648578","tid":1200982,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T01:38:38.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，已經安排好於本月底在日本舉行的二十國集團(G20)峰會上，與中國國家主席習近平會談，認為會發生有趣的事，拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普早前接受財經頻道CNBC訪問時威脅，如果在G20峰會上，未能與習近平達成貿易協議，美國將對中國實施新一輪關稅措施，亦即意味着華府仍有可能對餘下3000億美元中國貨，加徵25%關稅。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又強調，自己與習近平有良好的關係，而中方其實亦希望能達成貿易協議。"},{"pid":"3bc5169628d8b8d4a840384ca5a08ae4321ac40f","tid":1200982,"uid":55897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:39:12.000Z","msg":"成日靠外交部講,真係想聽係雜種講出口"},{"pid":"f3e4b2b05741deaadc9dec29663b8593ddeaba44","tid":1200982,"uid":216477,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ed326ba6866f700b9b2a8913cb98c4a7ebffe22","tid":1200982,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:44:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SongFei2017/status/1137019185647669250?s=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSongFei2017%2Fstatus%2F1137019185647669250%3Fs%3D17&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=ab05a428\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSongFei2017%2Fstatus%2F1137019185647669250%3Fs%3D17&h=8f016d8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SongFei2017/status/1137019185647669250?s=17</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ng20 撚狗示意圖"},{"pid":"497dfddb5bed089d54d19b88f48aea8357fda410","tid":1200982,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:58:54.000Z","msg":"反枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7a6850b0d36f80d808b99a16b3fc69a87496ec","tid":1200982,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0